 《我的化学浪漫》的弗兰克·伊罗在向埃隆·马斯克致敬后大声喊道：“操这个家伙” https://www.nme.com/news/music/my-chemical-romance-frank-iero-calls-out-elon-musk-controversial-saute-3830992?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=my-chemical-romance-弗兰克-埃罗-呼唤埃隆-马斯克-有争议的-敬礼Liberty DunworthWed, 22 Jan 2025 10:11:14 +0000 Music NewsNewsPoliticsDonald TrumpElon MuskEmoPop-Punk https://www.nme.com/?p=3830992 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elon-iero@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="埃隆·马斯克和弗兰克·伊罗" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elon-iero@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elon-iero@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elon-iero@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elon-iero@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elon-iero@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elon-iero@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “你的本色闪耀”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/my-chemical-romance-frank-iero-calls-out-elon-musk-controversial-salute-3830992">《My Chemical Romance》的弗兰克·伊罗 (Frank Iero) 在有争议的敬礼后喊道埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk)：“操这个家伙”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elon-iero@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="埃隆·马斯克和弗兰克·伊罗" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elon-iero@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elon-iero@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elon-iero@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elon-iero@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elon-iero@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elon-iero@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/my-chemical-romance">《我的化学浪漫》</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/frank-iero">弗兰克·伊罗</a>批评<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/elon-musk">埃隆·马斯克</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/donald-trump">唐纳德·特朗普</a>总统就职典礼上做出的有争议的举动。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/my-chemical-romance-new-song-the-foundations-of-decay-3224859"><b>我的化学浪漫的“腐烂的基础”是一次激烈、无畏的回归</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>该事件发生在周一（1月20日），当时当选总统第二次宣誓入主白宫。在就职典礼上，这位科技亿万富翁、SpaceX 和特斯拉首席执行官表达了他对<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/donald-trump-on-cusp-of-us-election-victory-entertainment-world-reacts-3809992">共和党胜利</a>的喜悦，并向人群发表了讲话。</p><p> “我只是想说谢谢你让这一切发生。”他说着， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/elon-musk-sparks-backlash-with-nazi-like-gesture-at-trump-inauguration-3830625">用右手拍着胸口，手掌向下，斜向上伸出手臂</a>。然后，X/Twitter 所有者转身对讲台后面的人群重复了这个手势。</p><p>许多人将这一手势比作纳粹敬礼，表示服从阿道夫·希特勒。</p><p> 《我的化学浪漫》的弗兰克·伊罗（Frank Iero）就是在这一举动中公开反对马斯克的人之一。昨晚（21 日），这位吉他手在 Instagram 上分享了这一被广泛电视转播的时刻的屏幕截图。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DFGvYlFxHbz/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6p